Dear {!Primary_Applicant_Name__c},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!!!

Congratulations on achieving another milestone in your home buying journey with us. We sincerely thank you for your continued payments towards your unit.

Please find the payment summary below for your reference:

Project: {!Project__r.Name}
Unit Number: {!Unit_No__r.Name}
Agreement Value (AV): ₹{!Allotment_Premium__c}
Total Payment Received: ₹{!RW_Total_Receipt_Amount_Received__c}
Payment % Achieved: {{Payment_Percentage}}%
Principal Amount Due: ₹{{Principal_Outstanding}}

We truly appreciate your trust in Runwal Enterprises and thank you for being a valued part of the Runwal family.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
